    Context variables required for this template:
    * courseid The id of the course data
    * coursename Course name
    * coursedescription Course summart
    * tablerender The render table with the entries
    * canaddentry If the user can add a new entry
    * addlink The link to add entry form

     Example context (json):
    {
        "courseid": 2,
        "coursename": "Test course",
        "coursedescription": "Lorem ipsum...",
        "tablerender": "Renderer table data",
        "canaddentry": true,
        "addlink": "#"
    }
}}
<div>
    <p>{{#str}} helloworld , tool_albertolarah , {{coursename}} {{/str}}</p>
    <p>{{{coursedescription}}}</p>
    {{#canaddentry}}
        <div><a role="button" href="{{addlink}}" class="btn btn-primary">{{#str}} newentry , tool_albertolarah {{/str}}</a></div>
    {{/canaddentry}}
    {{{tablerender}}}
    {{#canaddentry}}
        <div><a role="button" href="{{addlink}}" class="btn btn-primary">{{#str}} newentry , tool_albertolarah {{/str}}</a></div>
    {{/canaddentry}}
